## Usage

```ts
import { registerSearch, indexer, search, SearchQueryBuilder } from './src/search/index.js';

await registerSearch();
await indexer.indexOne({ id: '1', title: 'Red shoes' });

const built = SearchQueryBuilder.create('shoes').limit(10).build();
const result = await search.search(built.query, built.options);
```

## Providers

```bash
my add search --provider meilisearch
my add search --provider elasticsearch
my add search --provider algolia
```

Remote adapters fall back to the in-memory adapter when the SDK/host is unavailable.
